@Comment:	family is celebrating Fat's birthday. Chi , SIS and SIS2's voices are very hard to tell apart; there is very little speech attributed to Chi , which may or may not be her sisters; Bro's constant yelling and screaming also makes it hard to hear. In addition , the tape quality isn't wonderful. The radio is very loud in the background as well. Conversation is very splintered because of the multiple participants and interruptions such as phone calls and Bro: this makes distinguishing voices even harder; there are several strange breaks in the tape; Mot delivers several narratives near the beginning; family jargon happy is a present
